# Image Tampering Detection App

This application detects whether an uploaded image is tampered with by comparing it to a pre-stored original image. It uses **Python**, **Flask**, and **Pillow** for backend processing.

---

![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.8%2B-blue)
![Flask](https://img.shields.io/badge/flask-2.1-green)

